 《布鲁克林九九》主演安德烈·布劳尔去世，享年 61 岁https://www.nme.com/news/tv/andre-braugher-dead-brooklyn-9-9-captain-raymond-holt-3558099?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andre-braugher-dead-brooklyn-9-九队长雷蒙德霍尔特Eli OrdonezWed, 13 Dec 2023 02:51:57 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3558099 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安德烈·布劳尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>布劳尔的公关人员证实了这一消息</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/andre-braugher-dead-brooklyn-nine-nine-captain-raymond-holt-3558099">《布鲁克林九九》的主演安德烈·布劳尔 (Andre Brauger) 去世，享年 61 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安德烈·布劳尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/andre-braugher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>安德烈·布劳尔 (Andre Brauger) 去世，他因在 NBC 热门喜剧<i>《布鲁克林九九》</i>中扮演雷蒙德·霍尔特上尉而闻名<i>，</i>现已去世。他 61 岁了。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/andre-braugher-dead-brooklyn-nine-nine-1235835771/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Variety</i></a>和<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/andre-braugher-dead-homicide-life-on-the-street-1235747125/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《好莱坞报道》报道</i></a><i>，</i>布劳尔的长期经纪人詹妮弗·艾伦 (Jennifer Allen) 证实了布劳尔于周一（12 月 11 日）去世，她还补充说，布劳尔因“短暂的疾病”去世。他留下了他的妻子、女演员阿米·布拉布森和他的儿子迈克尔、以赛亚和约翰·韦斯利。</p><p>与布劳尔共事过的人们纷纷向他表示敬意。在<em>《布鲁克林九点九》</em>中饰演特里·杰福兹的特里·克鲁斯在 Instagram 上表达了哀悼。 “不敢相信你这么快就走了，”他写道。 “我很荣幸认识你，与你一起欢笑，与你共事，共同度过了辉煌的八年，见证了你无可替代的才华。这很伤人。你太早离开我们了。”</p><p>马克·埃文·杰克逊（Marc Evan Jackson）在<em>《布鲁克林九点九》</em>中饰演布劳尔的银幕丈夫，他简单地写道：“船长啊。我的船长。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0xpgZUxIXt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="